entries.femaleVariant: Capital is the blood of the global system of oppression!
Money is a tool used by the colonial oppressors of our minds!
[Disconnect from Net]
OK, so... If I'm gettin' this right... Someone hacked into this fortuneteller bot, rejigged its algorithm to spew out anti-establishment aphorisms instead of prophecies...
[Modify to generate nonsense]
Let your thoughts dance the lusty rumba while accompanied to a joyful accordion.
Success is the dilution of the soul!
The means of production should belong to the collective unconscious!
Class division is the breeding ground of anarchy!
Wait... What the hell is this?
[Pay to hear fortune]
Need to see what's inside.
You shall meet an attractive lobbyist when you least expect a violent outbreak of class warfare!
And then hooked it up to the net through a system of routers that masks the signal-origin. Pure fuckin' genius!
Become the obese narwhal in heat amidst the blazing ice.
Fox cubs are gathering data from the cesspit of the financial merry-go-round!
Look. Someone hooked Swedenborg up to the Net.
What're you waiting for? Let's see what secrets are flowin' in those cables.
Ugh, need to take a look. Somebody must've tampered with this thing...
entries.maleVariant: Need to take a look. Somebody must've tampered with this thing...

entries.femaleVariant: Huh. Trail cuts off here...
So, what... asshole hidin' here someplace?
Argh, maybe. Or maybe we get to another terminal. Have to see.
entries.maleVariant: Maybe. Or maybe we get to another terminal. Have to see.

entries.femaleVariant: Funny area, this. Kind of complements our guy's style, doesn't it?
Haha, seriously? What, you think you're gonna find a jack-in-a-box who wants to become a real boy? Haha!
Can we find whoever did this? I need to shake their hand.
Unlikely, for two reasons. First, they didn't leave a trace. Second... you're dead, Johnny.
Oh, right. When I get in a good mood, I forget that.
Hold on, I've got a better idea.
Cheap entertainment for braindead gonks, that's how.
How? This theme park another parody of capitalism run amok?
What it looks like – Swedenborg-Riviera! Ha! Come one, come all for the prophet of Night City! Ha!
Ohh... that's too good! A wind-up philosopher in a box! Hand me a couple eddies – see what he cranks out next!
How is this even possible?
How...? How's this even possible?
Your luck shall turn around when the means of production will flow on an endless stream of endorphins!
You scrollin' this? Heh, we need to save these for posterity's sake! Ha!
Not a fucking clue. But Jesus, V... how beautiful is this? Half the net's gettin' tweaked on wisdom from a puppet in a glass case – hairs are bein' split, spit is flyin' over interpretations...
Oh, man! Lemme tell you – fifty years of soul prison was worth it for this moment right here.
Hey, V... Don't turn it off, huh?
Eh, don't worry, Johnny. I'm not gonna take away Night City's philosopher of the people.
entries.maleVariant: Don't worry, Johnny. I'm not gonna take away Night City's philosopher of the people.

entries.femaleVariant: When a joke's been told a thousand times, it stops bein' funny.
No, no, V, wait! Ugh, you had to go and ruin everything.
Heh. Well, then! To Swedenborg-Riviera! Long may he live!
What the...? Ha! What'll all his fans think!
Oh, man... I know you and I don't always click, V, but I've gotta say... You've got your perks.
Let your thoughts dance the lusty rumba while accompanied to a joyful accordion.
Become the obese narwhal in heat amidst the blazing ice.
Behold his wounds, inflicted by a red panda – a soda-can lies nearby – the object of their passion!
Don't have any change.
Dammit... Don't got any change...
Money is the root of social entropy!
Chill. Not gonna ruin your fun.
